OL,3,CMohamed Al Fayed 'manipulated' Harrods
OL,4,Cmanagers to hide alleged sexual abuse
OL,6,FMr Al Fayed is accused of sexual
OL,7,Foffences against dozens of women but
OL,8,Fwas never charged while he was alive.
OL,10,FHe died last year aged 94.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, the Metropolitan Police
OL,13,Fsaid it had launched an investigation
OL,14,Finto more than five people who may
OL,15,Fhave "facilitated" his alleged crimes.
OL,17,FAn internal review is also being
OL,18,Fcarried out into how the force handled
OL,19,Fclaims about Mr Al Fayed while he was
OL,20,Falive.
