OL,4,Cmanagers to hide alleged sexual abuse
OL,6,FSince the latest publicity around the
OL,7,Fcase, 90 alleged victims have
OL,8,Fcontacted the Metropolitan Police to
OL,9,Fsay they fell prey to the tycoon, in
OL,10,Faddition to 21 alleged victims who had
OL,11,Falready contacted the force.
OL,13,FThe youngest of the 90 is thought to
OL,14,Fhave been 13 years old at the time she
OL,15,Fwas reportedly abused, and the alleged
OL,16,Fcrimes include rape and sexual assault.
OL,18,F"He tried to own you. And ultimately,
OL,19,FI got fired because I couldn't be
OL,20,Fbought," he said.
