OL,6,FMr Brilliant said he was "horrified"
OL,7,Fwhen he first heard the allegations
OL,8,Fthat Mr Al Fayed had abused hundreds
OL,9,Fof women.
OL,11,FMr Al Fayed acquired Harrods for #615
OL,12,Fmillion in 1985 and sold it to the
OL,13,FQatari royal family for a reported
OL,14,F#1.5 billion in 2010.
